A simple HTML page with JavaScript and CSS to convert temperatures between Fahrenheit and Celsius
This temperature converter features:

Two-way conversion between Fahrenheit and Celsius
Clean, responsive design with a modern UI
Input validation to ensure users enter valid numbers
Clear display of conversion results
The conversion formulas displayed at the bottom for reference

The interface is simple to use:

Enter a temperature in either the Fahrenheit or Celsius field
Click the corresponding conversion button
See the converted result both in the opposite field and in the result section

The calculations use the standard conversion formulas:

Celsius to Fahrenheit: (°C × 9/5) + 32
Fahrenheit to Celsius: (°F - 32) × 5/9
Preview(https://kwanelesishi.github.io/ConvertFahrenheitToCelsius/)
